      "writtenOn": "2016-11-07T17:34:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "nit: In CSV, records are separated by newlines and fields within a record are separated by commas. I think it will be easier to work with (e.g. editing the list in a text editor or spreadsheet) if each webpage is a different record (i.e. separated by newlines). I wouldn\u0027t even call it a CSV, although you could parse it as one if you want.",
