      "writtenOn": "2016-11-07T18:38:02Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I went with CSV to try to keep things compact. Pasting 40k webpages one per line in the text box seems to cause more crashiness than pasting 40k webpages on a single line separated by commas. Though the UI still seems to handle different kinds of inputs. Eg:\n\"\"\"\ntest1\ntest2\ntest3\ntest4\n\"\"\"\nand\n\"\"\"\ntest1,test2\ntest3,test4\n\"\"\"\nand\n\"\"\"\ntest1,test2,test3,test4\n\"\"\"\n\nDo you recommend I change \"Specify custom CSV of web pages\" to \"Specify custom list of web pages\"?",
